## 1. Архитектура

### Общая схема системы

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "🌐 Frontend"
        FE["Next.js 14<br/>Dashboard + Stream"]
    end
    
    subgraph "⚡ Backend"
        API["FastAPI<br/>REST + WebSocket"]
        Redis["Redis 7<br/>PubSub + Cache"]
        PG["PostgreSQL 15<br/>+ Alembic"]
    end
    
    subgraph "🤖 Agents"
        Android["Android Agent<br/>Kotlin + ADB"]
        PC["PC Agent<br/>Python + LDPlayer"]
    end
    
    subgraph "🔗 Integration"
        N8N["n8n<br/>Workflow Automation"]
        VPN["AmneziaWG<br/>VPN Overlay"]
    end
    
    subgraph "📊 Observability"
        Prom["Prometheus"]
        Graf["Grafana"]
        Alert["Alertmanager"]
    end
    
    FE <-->|"REST + WS"| API
    API <--> Redis
    API <--> PG
    API <-->|"WebSocket"| Android
    API <-->|"WebSocket"| PC
    API -->|"Webhooks"| N8N
    Android -.->|"WireGuard"| VPN
    API --> Prom --> Graf
    Prom --> Alert
```

### Технологический стек

| Слой | Технологии | Зачем |
|------|-----------|-------|
| **Database** | PostgreSQL 15 + SQLAlchemy 2.0 + Alembic | ACID, миграции, ORM |
| **Cache** | Redis 7 (PubSub + Key/Val + ZSet) | Real-time статус, очереди, каналы |
| **Backend** | FastAPI + Pydantic v2 + structlog | Async API, валидация, логи |
| **WebSocket** | FastAPI WS + async queues | Bidirectional, backpressure |
| **Streaming** | MediaCodec → H.264 → WebCodecs | Real-time видео 720p@30fps |
| **VPN** | AmneziaWG + Kill Switch | Обход блокировок, защита |
| **Android Agent** | Kotlin + Coroutines + OkHttp | ADB, Lua, OTA, DAG |
| **PC Agent** | Python + asyncio + psutil | LDPlayer, ADB Bridge, telemetry |
| **Automation** | n8n + TypeScript nodes | Low-code workflow |
| **Frontend** | Next.js 14 + TanStack Query + Zustand | SSR, реактивность, стейт |
| **Monitoring** | Prometheus + Grafana + Alertmanager | Метрики, дашборды, алерты |
| **CI/CD** | GitHub Actions + Docker Compose | Автоматизация, деплой |

