## 6. Стратегия Merge — 6 фаз

### Общий порядок

```mermaid
graph LR
    P1["Фаза 1<br/>Foundation"] --> P2["Фаза 2<br/>Backend Core"]
    P2 --> P3["Фаза 3<br/>Business Logic"]
    P3 --> P4["Фаза 4<br/>Agents"]
    P4 --> P5["Фаза 5<br/>Integration"]
    P5 --> P6["Фаза 6<br/>UI"]
    
    style P1 fill:#2d5016,color:#fff
    style P2 fill:#1a3a5c,color:#fff
    style P3 fill:#5c1a3a,color:#fff
    style P4 fill:#4a3a1a,color:#fff
    style P5 fill:#1a4a3a,color:#fff
    style P6 fill:#3a1a5c,color:#fff
```

