## 7. Тестирование — 5 уровней

### Пирамида тестов

```
         ╔═══════════╗
         ║   E2E     ║  ← Browser + Real API + Agents
         ╠═══════════╣
        ║ Integration ║  ← API + DB + Redis (docker)
        ╠═════════════╣
       ║  Contract     ║  ← JSON Schema matching
       ╠═══════════════╣
      ║  Component      ║  ← Service + Repository unit
      ╠═════════════════╣
     ║  Unit             ║  ← Pure functions, utils
     ╚═══════════════════╝
```

### Уровень 1 — Unit Tests

```bash
# Backend
pytest tests/unit/ -v --cov=backend --cov-report=term-missing

# Android
./gradlew testDebugUnitTest

# Frontend
npm run test -- --coverage
```

### Уровень 2 — Component Tests

```bash
# Backend service тесты с mock DB
pytest tests/component/ -v
```

### Уровень 3 — Contract Tests ⭐

```bash
# DAG Schema contract (TZ-04 ↔ TZ-07)
pytest tests/test_dag_contract.py -v

# Heartbeat contract (TZ-03 ↔ TZ-07)
pytest tests/test_heartbeat_contract.py -v

# API contract (OpenAPI spec)
npm run gen:types && npx tsc --noEmit   # TypeScript type check
```

### Уровень 4 — Integration Tests

```bash
# Полный стек в Docker
docker compose -f docker-compose.test.yml up -d
pytest tests/integration/ -v --timeout=60
```

### Уровень 5 — E2E Tests

```bash
# Playwright + Real backend
npx playwright test --headed
```

