## 8. CI/CD Pipeline

### GitHub Actions Workflow

```mermaid
graph LR
    PR["PR Created"] --> Lint["Lint + Format"]
    Lint --> Unit["Unit Tests"]
    Unit --> Build["Docker Build"]
    Build --> Integration["Integration Tests"]
    Integration --> Review["Code Review"]
    Review --> Merge["Merge to develop"]
    Merge --> Deploy["Deploy Staging"]
    Deploy --> E2E["E2E Tests"]
    E2E --> Promote["Promote to main"]
    
    style PR fill:#1a3a5c,color:#fff
    style Merge fill:#2d5016,color:#fff
    style Promote fill:#5c1a3a,color:#fff
```

### Файлы CI/CD

```
.github/workflows/
├── ci-backend.yml        # pytest + mypy + ruff
├── ci-frontend.yml       # vitest + tsc + eslint
├── ci-android.yml        # gradle test + lint
├── ci-pc-agent.yml       # pytest + mypy
├── ci-n8n.yml            # npm test + tsc
├── deploy-staging.yml    # docker compose up
└── deploy-production.yml # k8s apply
```

### Что проверяет CI при каждом PR

| Проверка | Инструмент | Обязательно |
|----------|-----------|------------|
| Python lint | `ruff check` | ✅ |
| Python types | `mypy --strict` | ✅ |
| Python tests | `pytest --cov=80` | ✅ |
| Kotlin lint | `ktlint` | ✅ |
| Kotlin tests | `./gradlew test` | ✅ |
| TS/JS lint | `eslint` | ✅ |
| TS types | `tsc --noEmit` | ✅ |
| Frontend tests | `vitest` | ✅ |
| Docker build | `docker build` | ✅ |
| Security scan | `trivy image` | ⚠️ Warning |

